          </div>
          <div class="bg-dark-900/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Technical Setup</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Get help overcoming setup roadblocks and permissions issues.</p>
          </div>
