            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üí°</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Monetization</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Discuss how to structure challenges or subscriptions for revenue.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What We'll Cover -->
        <div class="bg-dark-900/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-8">What We'll Cover in 15 Minutes</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-brand-green mt-1">‚úì</span>
                <span class="text-gray-300"><strong>Live Demo:</strong> See exactly how the bot works in a real server environment</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-brand-green mt-1">‚úì</span>
                <span class="text-gray-300"><strong>Setup Review:</strong> We'll look at your channel structure and permissions</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-brand-green mt-1">‚úì</span>
                <span class="text-gray-300"><strong>Revenue Plan:</strong> Estimate potential earnings from your specific member count</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-brand-green mt-1">‚úì</span>
                <span class="text-gray-300"><strong>Q&A:</strong> Ask any technical or business questions you have</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

